    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到混乱的世界</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/22de98644a0ca6ffbae3eeedc69a9712.poster.avif?t=1723791348\" width=616 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/22de98644a0ca6ffbae3eeedc69a9712.webm?t=1723791348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>冒险之旅：十字军东征是一款回合制策略游戏，设定在欧洲和中东十字军东征期间为背景。玩家将成为一名准备建立大帝国的野心家，想找机会侵略国土的邻居，贪欲的教团中生存，写下千秋万代王国的历史。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>又硬又软的图画</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/9354fddfe8da857f5c8354be82843621.poster.avif?t=1723791348\" width=616 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/9354fddfe8da857f5c8354be82843621.webm?t=1723791348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>我们首先画了又粗又直的外扩线，里面图画了个性充满的脸面。在单色背景前，使角色设计的更加生动。你看，他们会表示各自的喜怒哀乐，会生动的把剧情传给玩家。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>两种游戏模式</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/1840a89027891ed20f416437da5f2f00.poster.avif?t=1723791348\" width=616 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/1840a89027891ed20f416437da5f2f00.webm?t=1723791348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>我们有一个故事进行的剧情模式和随意占领全世界的沙盘模式。每一个模式都是相互连接的，会影响对方。玩家的选择和决定会引导你成功之路。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>朋友或敌人</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/d9fe789396edfa79bdfe2ce69cee8b03.poster.avif?t=1723791348\" width=616 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/d9fe789396edfa79bdfe2ce69cee8b03.webm?t=1723791348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>周围的王国会记住你的行动，会对应你的选择。大失措会引致纷争甚至战争。尊重他国，他们也会尊重我们。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>原罪</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/90c976e5f4a3a8c4871845a00d226e49.poster.avif?t=1723791348\" width=616 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/90c976e5f4a3a8c4871845a00d226e49.webm?t=1723791348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 在12世纪，没有宗教的人只是边界的野蛮人或即将要处于死刑的人而已。所有的王国都在一个宗教的影响之下，教团逐渐对王国要求证明他们的信心。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>阴谋和暗斗</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/fb93843f8f5262e852a1b58fb0ba81ae.poster.avif?t=1723791348\" width=616 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/fb93843f8f5262e852a1b58fb0ba81ae.webm?t=1723791348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在每年六月，分享同样宗教的王国会聚在一起互相批判。王国领导者批评对方，教团领导者终止战争-或要求圣战。为了得到其他参加者的支持，胁迫，贿赂等方式都可以。这些都是在以神的名义下允许的。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简单的选择，沉重的代价</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/6563a71e1f58157ae39e4fed4d383a42.poster.avif?t=1723791348\" width=616 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334310/extras/6563a71e1f58157ae39e4fed4d383a42.webm?t=1723791348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>战争前，玩家将会有很多选择。但一旦开始战争后，选择变得非常轻松。“要杀，或被杀！”",
